          "content": {
            "mimeType": "text/html; charset=UTF-8",
            "size": 8437,
            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n\n<title>Spellenspeciaalzaak Moenen &amp; Mariken Nijmegen</title>\n<meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"application/xhtml+xml; charset=UTF-8\" \\>\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n<!--tirei o meta, lembra-te de o trazer de volta-->\n\n<!--<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/editor.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/lightbox.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/profile.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/html.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/layout.css.php\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/form.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/borders.css.php\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/bammcms.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/menu.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/agenda.css\" media=\"screen, projection, tv\" \\>-->\n\n <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/foundation.min.css\" \\>\n <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/normalize.css\" \\>\n <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/css/styleMP.min.css\" \\>\n <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/slick/slick.css\" \\>\n\n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/menu.js\"> </script>\n<!--<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/lightbox_plus.js\"> </script>-->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/login.js\"> </script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/formdata2querystring.js\"> </script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/bammcms.js\"> </script>\n \n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/vendor/modernizr.js\"> </script>\n\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/x-icon\">\n<link rel=\"icon\" href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/x-icon\">\n\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"bodyWrapper\">\n        <header>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"logo small-12 columns\">\n                    <h1 class=\"text-center\">Moenen &amp; Mariken <span>Spellenspeciaalzaak</span></h1>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"small-12 columns\">\n                    <nav class=\"navBar\">\n                        <ul class=\"navLinks text-center\">\n                            <li class=\"hide-for-medium-up menuBtn\">&#9776; Menu</li>\n                            <li><a href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/\">Start</a></li>\n                            <li><a href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/producten\">Winkel+Webshop</a></li>\n                            <li><a href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/nieuw\"/>Nieuw</a></li>\n                            <li><a href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/activiteiten/\">Activiteiten</a></li>\n                            <li><a href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/info\">Contact</a></li>\n                            <li><a href=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/login\">Beheer</a></li>\n                            <li class=\"fbIcon\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Moenen.en.Mariken\" target=\"_blank\">f</a></li>\n                            \n                        </ul>\n                    </nav>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </header>\n        <div id=\"loadProductTop\"></div>\n        <div id=\"container\">\n            <div id=\"content\">\n              <div id=\"page_content\">\n    \n  <section>\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"small-12 columns text-center\">\n\t\t\t\t<article class=\"textBlock zoekLink\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Hieronder staan alle gevonden artikelen. Aangezien wij niet alles op voorraad kunnen hebben, kan het zijn dat je niet vindt wat je zoekt. Bel ons dan voor meer informatie, want misschien kunnen we het wel bestellen. De kleuren geven je meer informatie over de voorraad van de producten.  <br ><br ><a href=\"/producten/?new=1\">Zoek opnieuw</a><br ></p>\n\t\t\t\t</article>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</section>\n    <section class=\"resultsSection\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"small-12 columns text-center\">\n                <div class=\"textBlock\">\n                    <h2>ZOEK RESULTATEN</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"small-12 columns\">\n                <ul class=\"legenda text-center\">\n                    <li><span class=\"prodGreen\"></span>Product is op voorraad</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"prodYellow\"></span>Product binnenkort weer binnen</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"prodGrey\"></span>Product is te bestellen</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"small-12 columns resultsBox\">\n                 <div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"small-12 columns text-center\">\n          <b>[1]</b> \n    </div>\n</div>\n\n         <article class=\"product\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"medium-2 columns imgLink show-for-medium-up\">\n            <a href=\"javascript:popup('850032180863');\"><img src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/_productpics/850032180863.jpg\" \\></a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"small-7 medium-6 columns\">\n            <ul>\n                <li class=\"artikelname\"><a href=\"javascript:popup('850032180863');\">Vantage (ENG)</a></li>\n                <li>Vantage</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"small-5 medium-4 columns\">\n            <ul class=\"shoppingInfo\">\n                <li class=\"tr1 availability\" style=\"background-color:#FFA500;\"></li>\n                <li class=\"shoppingCart\"></li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"prodPrijs\">Prijs: &euro; 82,95</div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</article>\n\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n    <div class=\"small-12 columns text-center\">\n          <b>[1]</b> \n    </div>\n</div>\n\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n  \n  \n  \n\n</div>\n\n\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"nav\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <footer>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.manuelcalapez.com\" target=\"_blank\">front-end design and development by manuel calapez</a></p>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n    <script src=\"//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/tooltip/wz_tooltip.js\"> </script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/foundation.min.js\"> </script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/js/mainJS.min.js\"> </script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/includes/slick/slick.min.js\"> </script>\n \n    \n    \n    <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t/*function popup (code) {\n\t\timgWindow = window.open('http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/producten/details.php?code='+code, 'imgWindow', \n\t\t\t'width=450,height=450,scrollbars=yes');\n\t\timgWindow.focus();\n\t}*/\n    \n    function popup (code) {\n\t\tvar url = 'http://www.moenen-en-mariken.nl/producten/details.php?code='+code;\n        \n        $.get( url, function( data ) {\n            $( \"#loadProductTop\" ).html( data );\n        });\n        \n\t}\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>\n\n"
