            "text": "function herinnerMij() {\n\tvar answer = document.getElementById('HerinnerAnswer');\n\t\n\tdocument.getElementById('Herinner').click();\n\tif (answer.firstChild)\n\t   answer.removeChild(answer.firstChild); \n\n\tif (document.getElementById('Herinner').checked)\n\t   answer.appendChild(document.createTextNode('Ja')); \n\telse\n\t   answer.appendChild(document.createTextNode('Nee')); \n}\n"
